CAT is written in standard C++, so that it is readily compiled and platform-independent.

HOW TO INSTALL

1. For compilation, you need a GNU C++ compiler (g++/gcc). Please see more information at 
http://gcc.gnu.org/. 

2. Just type 'make' command to compile on your specific platform. That's it.


